Author: DolphinRabies
Text: It's perfectly okay to eat at maintenance when you're sick. Your body has been working really hard to fight off your sickness and it needs fuel to keep at it so you can get to feeling better. I know it's hard, but maybe start with some soup or something or maybe some crackers if that's safe for you?
